channel.title: How do you get inspired to work on a server?
channel.description: I really want to make a server. but im not inspired to do it. What are ways i can inspire myself?

item.title: How do you get inspired to work on a server?
item.dc:creator: @Ix_Soulcist_xI Soulcist
item.description:
@Ix_Soulcist_xI wrote:

I don’t know about being inspired. You would have to want to do it.

I’ll give this a shot though;

  1. You would learn some new things. This means thing a long the virtual world. You would also enhance computer skills, and learn programming.

  2. You would meet new people?

  3. You would be smarter than people at your school if you go to school?
